overview: In the very personal interview-auditions of Rocco's Intimate Castings 48, curious cuties and up-and-coming XXX starlets test their skills with international sex star Rocco Siffredi. We see their pretty, young bodies in motion, and we get to know their personalities as they open up for seductive, hugely hung Rocco.
title: Rocco's Intimate Castings 48
